Text: <c.bg_transparent>Who are you? What do you speak?</c.bg_transparent>

<c.bg_transparent>If you want to trade,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then you must meet our King Aelle.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We will take you to meet him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He wants to take us to meet his king.</c.bg_transparent>

<c.bg_transparent>Wait. It might help us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to go along with them.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Wait until we find out where we are.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm with Rollo. I say we kill them.</c.bg_transparent>

<c.bg_transparent>We all want peaceful trade</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with our neighbors,</c.bg_transparent>

<c.bg_transparent>-Offer them some money to go away.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-They're preparing some kind of ambush.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Let's kill them and be done with it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Come then. The royal villa is not far.</c.bg_transparent>
